oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Copy print of Private Norman Stewart
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Late 19th century copy print (8x10) of Pvt. Norman Stewart, Co. A, 189th NY Inf. Regt., USA. Pvt. Norman wears a short jacket issued by the State of New York as opposed to a garment issued by the Federal government.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Stewart, Norman
